MƆƆ BAEBOLO NE KA LA
DEBIE BIEKO BONI A YƐBAHOLA YƐAZUKOA YƐAVI BAEBOLO NE ANU A ?
ƐZINZALƐ ARANE ɛhye wula Gyihova Nyamenle , aleɛabo Tumivolɛ ne anyunlunyia .
Ɔka edwɛkpa ne ɔfa ɔkyekye menli rɛle kɛ ɔnrɛhyɛ Nyamenle anwuma Belemgbunlililɛ ne baye amumuyɛ kɔsɔɔti avi ɛkɛ na yeamaa azɛlɛ ye ahakyi paladaese .
Ɔmaa yɛnyia Gyisɛse Kelaese , mɔɔ wule amaa yɛanyia dahuu ngoane , na kɛkala ɔlɛdi tumi kɛ Nyamenle Belemgbunlililɛ ne azo Belemgbunli la anu diedi .
Sumunli 1879 , bɛhɔ zo bɛyɛ magazine ɛhye na bɛnva bɛnyɛ maanyɛlɛsɛm .
Nuhua edwɛkɛ ne amuala gyi Baebolo ne azo .
Bɛndɔne buluku ɛhye .
Ɔboka ewiade amuala Baebolo ngilehilelɛ gyima mɔɔ bɛfa ndoboa mɔɔ vi ahonle nu a bɛdi nwolɛ gyima la anwo .
Saa ɛbaye ndoboa a , yɛsɛlɛ wɔ kɔ www.jw.org azo anzɛɛ Belemgbunlililɛ Asalo mɔɔ bikye wɔ la .
Ɛleka mɔɔ NW li edwɛkɛ ne anzi la ɔkile kɛ ɔvi Nrelenza aneɛ nu New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures ne anu .
Edwɛkɛ mɔɔ doa zo la bɛahilehile nu .
